Thank you @girlsclubny for having me as a guest for your Grownish beauty panel. I loved talking to the girls and showing them the power of concealer! .. @shyyvonne asked me a question that really resonated with me. Don’t let social media make you feel less than. Most of the things you see is edited it’s not real life or real time. Beauty comes in all shades, shapes and sizes your imperfections are what make you perfect and unique .. you set your standard of what beauty is and don’t let anyone tell you otherwise #reneemadeulook ✨💫❤️

Side note my sister, Shyvonne is the Senior Manager of youth leadership & career pathways and she’s doing an amazing job with these girls it’s really inspiring. Shes doing a career exploration series weekly called “Grownish” & always looking for guests for interactive experiences. Shoot her a DM if you’re interested 💕

24 hours in Vegas 💃🏽

Fun Facts 

1. This was my first road trip from L.A to Vegas 

2. The sidekick was one of my favorite phones idk it was something about flippin the screen that made me feel like i was so cool lol … my ring tone and my voicemail song was “My boo” by @usher …. the Confessions album will always remind me of my 20’s #somanymemories 

3. This trip was very spontaneous and in my head I’m that girl but in real life I’m not lol I’m doing so good at just going with the flow and living my best life and i love that for me 🫶🏾

4. We all ended up on stage for the pre show i was twerkin on stage infront of thousands of people and the only thing i could think of is i hope my parents never see this 😩😩😩 *sidenote none of us got video of that moment so if anyone was at the Usher concert in Vegas on March 11th and took video of us 🤳🏾please DM me 🙏🏾

4. I can’t hang with @msamberpriley her energy is on another level they need to bottle up whatever she got going on and sell it 🤣
 
5. @briasamone you are my spirit animal 💫because the way you took over the stage and had the crowd going CRAZY was the highlight of my night!!!! 🙌🏾🙌🏾🙌🏾

We had SO MUCH FUN #theend
